#: ../../language/introduction.md:1
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "はじめに"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:3
msgid "A MoonBit program consists of top-level definitions including:"
msgstr "MoonBit プログラムは、次のようなトップレベル定義から構成されます："

#: ../../language/introduction.md:5
msgid "type definitions"
msgstr "型定義"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:6
msgid "function definitions"
msgstr "関数定義"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:7
msgid "constant definitions and variable bindings"
msgstr "定数定義と変数束縛"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:8
msgid "`init` functions, `main` function and/or `test` blocks."
msgstr "`init` 関数、`main` 関数、`test` ブロック"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:10
msgid "Expressions and Statements"
msgstr "式と文"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:12
msgid ""
"MoonBit distinguishes between statements and expressions. In a function "
"body, only the last clause should be an expression, which serves as a return"
" value. For example:"
msgstr "MoonBit では文と式を区別します。関数本体では最後の句だけが式であり、それが戻り値になります。例えば："

#: ../../language/introduction.md:14
msgid ""
"fn foo() -> Int {\n"
"  let x = 1\n"
"  x + 1\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn bar() -> Int {\n"
"  let x = 1\n"
"  //! x + 1\n"
"  x + 2\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"fn foo() -> Int {\n"
"  let x = 1\n"
"  x + 1\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn bar() -> Int {\n"
"  let x = 1\n"
"  //! x + 1\n"
"  x + 2\n"
"}"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:28
msgid "Expressions include:"
msgstr "式には次のものが含まれます："

#: ../../language/introduction.md:30
msgid ""
"Value literals (e.g. Boolean values, numbers, characters, strings, arrays, "
"tuples, structs)"
msgstr "値リテラル（例：真偽値、数値、文字、文字列、配列、タプル、構造体）"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:31
msgid "Arithmetical, logical, or comparison operations"
msgstr "算術演算、論理演算、比較演算"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:32
msgid ""
"Accesses to array elements (e.g. `a[0]`), struct fields (e.g `r.x`), tuple "
"components (e.g. `t.0`), etc."
msgstr "配列要素（例：`a[0]`）、構造体フィールド（例：`r.x`）、タプル要素（例：`t.0`）などへのアクセス"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:33
msgid "Variables and (capitalized) enum constructors"
msgstr "変数と（先頭が大文字の）enum コンストラクタ"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:34
msgid "Anonymous local function definitions"
msgstr "無名ローカル関数定義"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:35
msgid "`match`, `if`, `loop` expressions, etc."
msgstr "`match`、`if`、`loop` 式など"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:37
msgid "Statements include:"
msgstr "文には次のものが含まれます："

#: ../../language/introduction.md:39
msgid "Named local function definitions"
msgstr "名前付きローカル関数定義"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:40
msgid "Local variable bindings"
msgstr "ローカル変数束縛"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:41
msgid "Assignments"
msgstr "代入"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:42
msgid "`return` statements"
msgstr "`return` 文"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:43
msgid "Any expression whose return type is `Unit`, (e.g. `ignore`)"
msgstr "戻り値の型が `Unit` の式（例：`ignore`）"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:45
msgid ""
"A code block can contain multiple statements and one expression, and the "
"value of the expression is the value of the code block."
msgstr "コードブロックには複数の文と 1 つの式を含められ、その式の値がコードブロックの値になります。"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:47
msgid "Variable Binding"
msgstr "変数束縛"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:49
msgid ""
"A variable can be declared as mutable or immutable using `let mut` or `let`,"
" respectively. A mutable variable can be reassigned to a new value, while an"
" immutable one cannot."
msgstr ""
"変数は `let mut` または `let` "
"を使って、それぞれ可変または不変として宣言できます。可変変数には新しい値を再代入できますが、不変変数にはできません。"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:51
msgid "A constant can only be declared at top level and cannot be changed."
msgstr "定数はトップレベルでのみ宣言でき、変更できません。"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:53
msgid ""
"let zero = 0\n"
"\n"
"const ZERO = 0\n"
"\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  //! const ZERO = 0 \n"
"  let mut i = 10\n"
"  i = 20\n"
"  println(i + zero + ZERO)\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"let zero = 0\n"
"\n"
"const ZERO = 0\n"
"\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  //! const ZERO = 0 \n"
"  let mut i = 10\n"
"  i = 20\n"
"  println(i + zero + ZERO)\n"
"}"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:68
msgid "A top level variable binding"
msgstr "トップレベルの変数束縛は、"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:69
msgid ""
"requires **explicit** type annotation (unless defined using literals such as"
" string, byte or numbers)"
msgstr "**明示的な**型注釈が必要です（文字列、バイト、数値などのリテラルで定義する場合を除く）"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:70
msgid "can't be mutable (use `Ref` instead)"
msgstr "可変にはできません（代わりに `Ref` を使ってください）"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:74
msgid "Naming conventions"
msgstr "命名規則"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:76
msgid ""
"Variables, functions should start with lowercase letters `a-z` and can "
"contain letters, numbers, underscore, and other non-ascii unicode chars. It "
"is recommended to name them with snake_case."
msgstr ""
"変数名と関数名は小文字の `a-z` で始める必要があり、文字、数字、アンダースコア、その他の非 ASCII Unicode "
"文字を含められます。snake_case を使うことを推奨します。"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:79
msgid ""
"Constants, types should start with uppercase letters `A-Z` and can contain "
"letters, numbers, underscore, and other non-ascii unicode chars. It is "
"recommended to name them with PascalCase or SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE."
msgstr ""
"定数名と型名は大文字の `A-Z` で始める必要があり、文字、数字、アンダースコア、その他の非 ASCII Unicode "
"文字を含められます。PascalCase または SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE を使うことを推奨します。"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:82
msgid "Keywords"
msgstr "キーワード"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:84
msgid "The following are the keywords and should not be used:"
msgstr "以下はキーワードであり、識別子として使用できません："

#: ../../language/introduction.md:86
msgid ""
"[\n"
"  \"as\", \"else\", \"extern\", \"fn\", \"fnalias\", \"if\", \"let\", "
"\"const\", \"match\", \"using\",\n"
"  \"mut\", \"type\", \"typealias\", \"struct\", \"enum\", \"trait\", "
"\"traitalias\", \"derive\",\n"
"  \"while\", \"break\", \"continue\", \"import\", \"return\", \"throw\", "
"\"raise\", \"try\", \"catch\",\n"
"  \"pub\", \"priv\", \"readonly\", \"true\", \"false\", \"_\", \"test\", "
"\"loop\", \"for\", \"in\", \"impl\",\n"
"  \"with\", \"guard\", \"async\", \"is\", \"suberror\", \"and\", \"letrec\","
" \"enumview\", \"noraise\",\n"
"  \"defer\",\n"
"]\n"
msgstr ""
"[\n"
"  \"as\", \"else\", \"extern\", \"fn\", \"fnalias\", \"if\", \"let\", "
"\"const\", \"match\", \"using\",\n"
"  \"mut\", \"type\", \"typealias\", \"struct\", \"enum\", \"trait\", "
"\"traitalias\", \"derive\",\n"
"  \"while\", \"break\", \"continue\", \"import\", \"return\", \"throw\", "
"\"raise\", \"try\", \"catch\",\n"
"  \"pub\", \"priv\", \"readonly\", \"true\", \"false\", \"_\", \"test\", "
"\"loop\", \"for\", \"in\", \"impl\",\n"
"  \"with\", \"guard\", \"async\", \"is\", \"suberror\", \"and\", \"letrec\","
" \"enumview\", \"noraise\",\n"
"  \"defer\",\n"
"]\n"

#: ../../language/introduction.md:97
msgid "Reserved Keywords"
msgstr "予約語"

